{"tid":1336261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦","createTime":"2019-07-21T00:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T03:12:17.000Z","uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4844edbede40f92472e440bd14f162f310fdc6","tid":1336261,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T00:57:00.000Z","msg":"最近成日<br />\n突然間個人 down哂/hang機.<br />\n<br />\n訓到超多<br />\n(試過有幾日，十幾個鐘咁訓...)<br />\n<br />\n又暈又作嘔，有時嗰心仲突然跳到超大聲。<br />\n(E幾個情形 又會導致上面down / hang的情形.)<br />\n(相反，如果去諗點解/發生咩事而down/ hang，又會突然開始作嘔)<br />\n<br />\n無哂時間觀念分唔到日期。<br />\n(同訓教時間亂哂有關。)<br />\n<br />\n訓完都仲想訓，唔識餓。<br />\n起身嗰分幾鐘會好精神，非常咁精神。<br />\n但幾分鐘之後又會想訓/暈。"},{"pid":"5cd06293836fb5db23f113337e71c225939c10da","tid":1336261,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T00:59:01.000Z","msg":"飲咖啡等，只會令個人好易醒同埋會發夢。<br />\n但一樣會想訓...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暈同嘔 已經比家人笑係咪係咪有咗。<br />\n(利申無可能)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3e2288130099b1809ea1bcede4029c78d8235a","tid":1336261,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T01:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人知點搞"},{"pid":"fb382743336d23391d77b1f9400a45f4dccb2ffe","tid":1336261,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:00:39.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪本身有其他病要長期食藥？<br />\n冇既真係睇下中醫調理下好<br />\n咖啡唔好亂飲<br />\n我自己就好易咖啡因中毒<br />\n飲完頭暈，心跳加速，極度眼訓<br />\n唔知你會唔會<br />\n同埋你係咪有食開精神科藥物？"},{"pid":"f9fedc181e2342061443f59580bdebb643d68ea8","tid":1336261,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb382743336d23391d77b1f9400a45f4dccb2ffe","tid":1336261,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:00:39.